    <div class="tit" style="position: relative;top:3vw;margin-bottom: 1vw;margin-top: 2vw;">
        Guidelines  for  Indoor  Sports Complex
    </div>
    <div class="welcome" style="position: relative;margin-top:5vw ;">
    The following guidelines are established to <b>ensure the safe, efficient, and respectful use of the
    Indoor Sports Complex.</b> These guidelines apply to all users, including students, faculty, staff,
    and visitors. Violations of these guidelines may result in <b>disciplinary action,</b> including suspension
    of access privileges
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="welcome">
    
        <div class="order">
            1. Gym Guidelines
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Access:</div> The gym is accessible only to registered users with valid ID cards.</div></li>
                <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Dress Code:</div> Appropriate gym attire and non-marking/gym/weightlifting gum sports
                    shoes are mandatory.</div></li>
                <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Time Limit:</div> During peak hours, limit the use of cardio machines to 30 minutes per user.</div></li>
                <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Personal Belongings:</div>Avoid bringing valuables <div class="uorder">Lockers are available and must be
                    used responsibly(not available from 16).</div> .</div></li>
                <li><div class="uorder">Conduct:</div> <ul style="position: relative;left: 5vw;"><li>No loud music or disruptive behavior</li>  <li>Respect fellow gym users and follow instructions from gym staff.</li></ul>
                <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Behavior:</div> Carry your own towel to maintain proper hygiene.</div></li>    
        </ul>
    
</div>

    
<div class="welcome">
    
        <div class="order">2. Indoor Games Area Guidelines (Chess, Carrom, etc.)

        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Access:</div> Only registered users with valid ID cards are permitted.</div></li>
                
                <li><div class="uorder">Equipment Care:</div> <ul style="position: relative;left: 5vw;"> <li>Use the provided equipment responsibly.</li>  <li>Report any damages immediately to the staff.</li></ul></li>
                <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Time Limit:</div><div class="uorder">Sessions are limited to 45 minutes to 1 hour when others are waiting.</div>.</div></li>
                <li><div class="uorder">Cleanliness:</div> <ul style="position: relative;left: 5vw;"><li>Maintain cleanliness and dispose of waste properly.</li>  <li>No food or drinks are allowed in the gaming area.</li></ul>
