            <div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Access:</div> Users must book slots in advance and carry valid ID cards.</div></li>
            <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Footwear:</div> Non-marking sports shoes are mandatory..</div></li>
            <li><div class="uorder">Equipment:</div> <ul style="position: relative;left: 5vw;"><li>Users must bring their rackets and balls.</li>  <li>Handle tables and nets with care.</li></ul>
