<div class="welcome">
    
    <div class="order">
        General Rules for the Indoor Sports Complex
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Safety First:</div>  Report any injuries or equipment malfunctions immediately.</div></li>
            <li><div style="display: flex;gap:0.5vw;"> <div class="uorder">Respect Timings:</div> The complex operates during designated hours. Users must adhere
            to their allotted slots.</div></li>
